## Hedging to Reduce

One qualifier per claim is plenty. Cut excessive stacks like "could potentially possibly might."

| Stacked Hedge | Fix |
|---|---|
| "It could potentially possibly be argued that..." | "Some argue..." or just state the claim |
| "might possibly..." | "might..." |
| "I think maybe perhaps..." | "I think..." |
